org.lukep.javavis.metrics
Interface IMeasurableNode

All Superinterfaces:
IGenericModelNode, java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClassModel, MethodModel, PackageModel, ProjectModel, VariableModel
public interface IMeasurableNode
extends IGenericModelNode

Represents a single node that is able to have IMeasurableVisitors visit and apply metric measurements upon it.
